Description:
Feel Right At Home On Almost ½ An Acre!
This is the perfect opportunity for you to move into your new home with absolutely nothing to do. This neat 3 bedroom cedar home nestled on an elevated 1693m2 property that is perfectly maintained with all services connected & is within walking distance to the shops, transport, childcare & tennis courts. All this sets the scene for a relaxing lifestyle in the hills. Perfectly presented throughout, the home offers a crackling wood fire, polished floorboards, ensuite to main plus a sunny deck area which features a lovely view over the valley. Fully fenced with a double carport, double garage, sealed driveway & outdoor covered entertaining area - what more could you possibly want - call us & inspect today!!!

Description:
Large Family Home on ½ Acre
With two large living areas, spacious new kitchen and freshly modern bathroom, this large light-filled home is sure to impress the whole family. The home offers a WIR large enough to use as a nursery, ensuite, BIR's in all other bedrooms, plenty of internal storage and a study with external access perfect for a home office. Other features include a Coonara, GWH, reverse cycle air conditioner, double glazed windows in the living area and master bedroom & solar heat pump hot water service. Outside you will find a large decked entertaining area, family friendly play area with cubby house, multiple fruit trees, 25,000ltr water tank with home supply as well as mains supply, carport and a workshop to keep everyone in the family happy. Call to inspect today!

Description:
Room To Move On Almost 1/2 An Acre
This charming hills home is nestled amongst flourishing landscaped gardens and large lawn areas on an idyllic allotment of almost 1/2 acre. Large windows allow plenty of natural light to flow through the home and capture the true essence of hills living. Open plan lounge and dining room is overlooked by the kitchen and ensures that entertaining is a breeze for the whole family. The home also features 3 bedrooms, polished hardwood floors, coonara, gas ducted heating, air conditioning and large covered entertaining area. Take advantage of the fully fenced block and extras that include triple carport, garden shed, chicken run, veggie patch, fruit trees, water tank, storage area and all of this with sealed road access..

Description:
Perfect In Everyway!
Immaculately presented, this family home has a warm & welcoming atmosphere as soon as you walk through the front door.
The large windows allow plenty of natural light to stream in & offer a picturesque view of the garden from every room.
Offering spacious living areas, the family room has a cosy open fire which is perfect for wintery afternoons, formal dining area with coonara & a great sized kitchen with breakfast bar & adjoining meals area.
The master bedroom is complete with walk in robe, huge ensuite with spa & sliding doors which lead out to a paved courtyard.
Outside you will discover a useable & fully fenced yard, almost
an acre of landscaped gardens with pond & waterfall & wood shed.
The double garage has concrete floor & power as well as internal access to the house & remote garage doors.
There is also ample under-house storage, cellar & gas ducted throughout.
Don't miss out on this one!

Description:
First In Best Dressed!
Nestled away in a quiet part of town sits this large home ready to welcome a new family! The perfect lifestyle awaits with plenty of space for everyone. Featuring a large family room, large new open plan kitchen-diner with granite bench tops and quality stainless steel appliances alongside added bonuses such as gas ducted heating throughout, split system heating and cooling to lounge.
The cathedral ceilings and exposed beams add loads of character and charm.
There are four good sized bedrooms with built in robes, family bathroom with separate toilet and a separate laundry with external access. Outside offers a wrap-around veranda with a fantastic decked entertaining area that overlooks the usable 1/4 acre, a fully fenced yard , single carport, two sheds and plenty of under-house storage complete with a large workshop.
With just a few finishing touches, this home makes for comfortable living for the whole family.

Description:
On Top Of The World On Over 37 Acres
Spanning over 40 squares under roofline, this mud brick, steel frame home oozes character throughout with brick flooring, high ceilings & wonderful views across lush green pastures of Cardinia & Westernport Bay. The double glazed windows provide excellent energy efficiency & allow plenty of natural light to shine through the open plan living areas. There are 4 double size bedrooms, plus study or rumpus area for the kids, plus a spacious living/family area which is ideal for formal or informal entertaining. Beautiful gardens surround the home & provide colour all year round to enjoy. There is a dam, a natural spring, a large 15x6 mtr shed for the home handyman, solar panels to ensure an energy efficient lifestyle & 37 acres of paradise to pursue any interest you desire. This is a place for relaxation away from the hustle & bustle of everyday life, call today to inspect & you will feel on top of the world!
